tables.table_schema:
CREATE TABLE PatientOutcomes (
  patient_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  surgery_date DATE,
  outcome_description TEXT,
  recovery_rate DECIMAL(5,2)
)

CREATE TABLE robotic_surgery_procedures (
  procedure_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  procedure_name TEXT,
  surgeon_name TEXT,
  procedure_date DATE,
  success_rate DECIMAL
);

CREATE TABLE patient_records (
  patient_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  procedure_date DATE,
  outcome VARCHAR(50),
  recovery_days INT
)

CREATE TABLE surgical_team (
  team_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  surgeon_name VARCHAR(50),
  nurse_name VARCHAR(50),
  assistant_name VARCHAR(50)
)

CREATE TABLE surgery_procedures (
  procedure_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  procedure_name VARCHAR(50),
  surgical_team_id INT,
  FOREIGN KEY (surgical_team_id) REFERENCES surgical_team(team_id)
)

CREATE TABLE recovery_data (
  recovery_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  patient_id INT,
  recovery_date DATE,
  recovery_status VARCHAR(50),
  FOREIGN KEY (patient_id) REFERENCES patient_records(patient_id)
)
CREATE TABLE patient_data (id INT PRIMARY KEY, patient_name STRING, surgery_date DATE, recovery_rate FLOAT);
CREATE TABLE surgery_procedure (id INT PRIMARY KEY, procedure_name STRING, surgeon_name STRING, procedure_date DATE);
CREATE TABLE complication_data (id INT PRIMARY KEY, patient_id INT, complication_name STRING, complication_date DATE);
CREATE TABLE recovery_data (id INT PRIMARY KEY, patient_id INT, recovery_status STRING, recovery_date DATE);
CREATE TABLE surgeon_data (id INT PRIMARY KEY, surgeon_id INT, surgeon_name STRING);
